snippet.title: The Sims 4 Jungle Adventure: Explore Selvadorada Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
See what Selvadorada has to offer as your Sims explore a unique wilderness landscape, revealing a temple, jungle obstacles, cursed relics, and treasures. Experience the culture and customs, from devouring local eats to learning spicy dance moves!

Now available for PC and Mac.

Learn more about this Game Pack: http://x.ea.com/44816.


*REQUIRES THE SIMS 4 GAME (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES TO PLAY. SEE www.thesims.com/system-requirements FOR MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR THIS PACK.
